16
00:00:38,690 --> 00:00:39,690
The good news

17
00:00:39,690 --> 00:00:41,940
is that North Korea isn’t especially successful

18
00:00:41,940 --> 00:00:43,409
at testing missiles.

19
00:00:43,409 --> 00:00:44,409
However,

20
00:00:44,409 --> 00:00:46,359
this is one more step towards developing

21
00:00:46,359 --> 00:00:49,920
a nuclear warhead that can reach the US.

22
00:00:49,920 --> 00:00:53,149
